TheSiege Privacy policy 
From this moment TheSiege producer is refrenced as  AmethystGames.

App only collects data about user engagment and location through our advertisers.

AmethystGames is not responsible for any lost data including TheSiege username or place in leaderboard.
AmethystGames is not responsible for any ads that are shown to the players.
AmethystGames does not take responsibility if this document is not avaible in case of (github.com) failure.
AmethystGames can change privacy policy at any time but MUST post an information on google play store page.

